title: Kevin Love makes his debut, but Cleveland Cavaliers still lose to Toronto Raptors 87-81
text:
Published By: Cleveland.com: Cavaliers - Today 
Kevin Love finally made his long-awaited debut, but his presence couldn't prevent an 87-81 loss to the Raptors....
